latestIgtvVideos.title: @tiasaray - I’m Going Down (Original)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
WATCH ON FULL FRAME ✨ written and composed by yours truly 🌝 

story : right before your spiritual awakening, demons may try to get a hold of you, seduce you, and manipulate you. I had my own haunting experiences and somehow the Universe got a tighter hold of me, you may call it God, Higher Power, Krishna, or Shambo. and I trusted my instinct, my higher self. 
here I am now on a greater path where fame, glitz, and glamour don't tempt me anymore. I am here to serve, experience life, and gain wisdom and share. 
You may ask What am I doing with my life? 
I would say "Just living more consciously in the 'now', rest I will figure out by time."
here's a song for you that you always wanted. farewell, lucifer. I don't want my California dreams anymore. For I am more than this body and I am more than my mind.
